<style>
body
{
background-image:url('/bgpic.jpg');
background-repeat:no-repeat;
background-size: cover;
}
</style>

<div style="text-align:center">
  <font color="white"><h1><br><br><br>많은 사람들이 벌써<br>그루퍼를 이용해 팀플을 시작하고 있어요</h1></font>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-4">
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-body">
          <p>누구나 효율적인 팀플을 원합니다. 여기 실시간 의사결정과 파일을 공유할 수 있는 서비스가 있습니다. 이메일을 적고 바로 이용해보세요!
          </p>
          <form id="regmail" class="form-inline" action="/test/regmail" method="post">
            <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token -%>
            <div class="field">
              <input class="form-control" id="user_email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="이메일" required/>
              <input type="submit" class="btn btn-new" role="button" value="시작하기">
            </div>
          </form>
          <h4><small>입력한 이메일로 가입 링크가 전송됩니다.
            <a class="" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">로그인하기</a>
          </small></h4>
          
          <!--
          <form class="form-inline" action="/test/index" method="post">
            <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token -%>

            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputName2" placeholder="팀 이름" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">팀 만들기</button>
          </form>
          -->
          
          
          <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
            <div style="text-align:center">
              <div class="row">
                <hr />
                <div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2">
                  <h2 style="margin-top: 0px;">로그인</h2>
                  <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="field">
                      <input class="form-control" id="user_email" name="user[email]" type="email" placeholder="이메일" autofocus/>
                    </div>
          
                    <div class="field">
                      <input class="form-control" id="user_password" name="user[password]" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호" autocomplete="off"/>
                    </div>
                    <!--
                    <% if devise_mapping.rememberable? -%>
                      <div class="field">
                        <%= f.check_box :remember_me %>
                        아이디 기억하기
                      </div>
                    <% end -%>
                    -->
                    <br>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-new" style="width: 100%;">로그인</button>
                  </div>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>